    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Emeritus professor Darlington received his B.A. from Swarthmore College 1959, and his Ph.D. from the University of Minnesota in 1963. He has been teaching in Cornell's Psychology Department since 1963.</p>  </bioghist>
